  "title": "🇸🇬 Events & Marketing (Entry Level Welcome)",
  "description": "<h1><u>Brand Ambassador</u> (Full-Time)</h1><h3>🇸🇬 Singapore</h3><p>We’re looking for confident, outgoing individuals to represent exciting client brands at events and roadshows. If you enjoy meeting people, communicating, and building experiences, this role is for you.</p><h3>What You’ll Do?</h3><ul><li>🌟 Represent our client brands professionally at events & roadshows</li><li>🗣 Communicate product features and brand value clearly</li><li>🤝 Engage with customers and create positive experiences</li><li>👥 Work closely with a dynamic, high-energy team<br /><br /><u><strong>Who We’re Looking For?</strong></u></li></ul><ul><li>🗣 Confident and comfortable speaking to people</li><li>😊 Positive, professional, and well-presented</li><li>🤝 Enjoys interacting and building connections</li><li>💪 Self-motivated and willing to learn</li></ul><p><u><strong>What You’ll Gain?</strong></u></p><ul><li>🌟 Hands-on brand representation experience</li><li>📈 Strong communication & presentation skills</li><li>🚀 Leadership development & career progression</li><li>🌍 Local & overseas travelling opportunities</li></ul><p><u><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></u></p><p>You’ll gain real-world experience working with top brands while developing skills that are valuable for sales, marketing, leadership, and entrepreneurship — all in a fun, fast-paced environment.</p>",
